  - id: 55
    questionText:
      en: But Chief, what are you thinking?..
      native: "Ale\u017C Wodzu, co W\xF3dz?.."
    questionVisual: {fileID: 2800000, guid: a87da26556fdfa84f941c826b24365d6, type: 3}
    answer0:
      en: ...well, in that case, I apologize.
      native: ... to ja przepraszam.
    answer0_Image: {fileID: 0}
    answer1:
      en: ...don't overdo it, Chief!
      native: "...niech W\xF3dz nie przesadza!"
    answer1_Image: {fileID: 0}
    answer2:
      en: ...again with the same thing?
      native: ...znowu o tym samym?
    answer2_Image: {fileID: 0}
    answer3:
      en: ...I'm only joking, after all.
      native: "... przecie\u017C ja tylko \u017Cartuj\u0119."
    answer3_Image: {fileID: 0}
    useQuestionAnswer: 1
    correctIndices: 00000000
    useImageAnswers: 0
  - id: 56
    questionText:
      en: Just like people, Funky...
      native: Tak samo jak ludzie, Funky...
    questionVisual: {fileID: 0}
    answer0:
      en: ...without any difference.
      native: "...bez \u017Cadnej r\xF3\u017Cnicy"
    answer0_Image: {fileID: 0}
    answer1:
      en: ..always lie to your face.
      native: "...zawsze k\u0142ami\u0105 w oczy."
    answer1_Image: {fileID: 0}
    answer2:
      en: ...know no mercy.
      native: "...nie znaj\u0105 lito\u015Bci."
    answer2_Image: {fileID: 0}
    answer3:
      en: ...are only looking for profit.
      native: "...szukaj\u0105 tylko zysku."
    answer3_Image: {fileID: 0}
    useQuestionAnswer: 0
    correctIndices: 00000000
    useImageAnswers: 0
